<H3> <TI>   National Assembly Scheduled To Meet 5 Apr </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    National Assembly Scheduled To Meet 5 Apr </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0104140594 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 1100 GMT 1 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0104140594 </F>
<F P=104>  Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 1100 GMT 1 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=105> Cambodian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Communique" issued in Phnom Penh on 31 March] </F>
  [Text] The National Assembly Secretariat is honored to 
inform the public that the second session of the National 
Assembly's first legislature will be held on Tuesday, 5 April 
1994, at 0800 at the National Assembly. 
  At this plenary session, the Assembly will listen to a 
message from His Majesty King Norodom Sihanouk of the Kingdom of 
Cambodia; a report on the activities of the National Assembly 
Standing Committee; and debate and decide on the invalidation of 
National Assembly members' status and the validity of new 
Assembly members. 
  The public is hereby informed. 
  [Dated] Phnom Penh, 31 March 1994 

</TEXT>

