BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 3 (KCNA) -- Some 500 students 
staged a strong anti-U.S. demonstration at a park in central 
Seoul on April 2, protesting the U.S. plans to deploy Patriot 
missiles in South Korea, according to a foreign press report 
from Seoul. 
