<H3> <TI>   Conference of Party Cell Secretaries Concludes </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Conference of Party Cell Secretaries Concludes </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Delegates Named Labor Heros </H4>

<F P=102> SK0404070794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0515 GMT 4 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0404070794 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 4 (KCNA) -- A ceremony was held 
here Sunday to confer the title of Labour Hero of the DPRK on 
delegates to the national conference of party cell secretaries. 
  Present at the ceremony were secretary of the C.C. [Central 
Committee], the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] Kye Ung-tae and 
chief secretary of the South Pyongan Provincial party committee 
So Yun-sok who are Politburo members of the WPK Central 
Committee, officials concerned and the delegates to the 
conference. 
  The title of Labour Hero of the Republic was conferred on 
Hong Chong-ok, Yi Kang-ha and An Pyong-ok who, working as party 
cell secretary for many years, had enhanced the militant 
function and role of party organizations and actively aroused 
party members to the revolution and construction with unfailing 
loyalty to the party and the leader, thus greatly contributing 
to strengthening the singlehearted unity of the whole society. 

</TEXT>

