<F P=100> Vietnam </F>
<H3> <TI>   Nong Duc Manh Received Iranian Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Nong Duc Manh Received Iranian Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0204150294 Hanoi VNA in English 1448 GMT 2 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK0204150294 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA April 2 -- Chairman of the National 
Assembly Nong Duc Manh received here today a delegation of the 
Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs of Iran led by its 
Minister Hoseyn Kamali. 
  Vietnamese Minister of Labour, War Invalids and Social 
Affairs Tran Dinh Hoan was also present at the reception. 
Chairman Nong Duc Manh and Minister H. Kamali compared notes on 
the friendly relations between the two peoples and the 
cooperation between the two countries. 
  Chairman Nong Duc Manh affirmed that the Vietnam National 
Assembly would do its utmost to carry out documents initialed by 
Vietnam and Iran. He also wished for the further development of 
the friendship and cooperation between the two countries. 

</TEXT>

