<H4>    SRV Prime Minister Arrives </H4>

<F P=102> BK0204090294 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 0500 GMT 2 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0204090294 </F>
<F P=104>  Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 0500 GMT 2 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=105> Cambodian </F>


