<H3> <TI>   Geological Service Produces Minerals Map </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Geological Service Produces Minerals Map </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW0204155894 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1311 GMT 2 Apr 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW0204155894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 2 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- As the 
Geological Service informs, it has accomplished the making of a 
hydrogeological map of minerals the scale 1:1000000. The map 
establishes about 800 deposits of minerals. Such a map is 
issued in Mongolia for the first time with own forces. 

</TEXT>

