<H3> <TI>   Legislators: Hosokawa Desires `To Step Down' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Legislators: Hosokawa Desires `To Step Down' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW0504140094 Tokyo KYODO in English 1351 GMT 5 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0504140094 </F>
