work of CVW's echelons. He analyzed the significant position of 
the CVW organizations as well as their role in promoting 
national industrialization and implementing the new economic 
management system. 
  Comrade Do Muoi said: The CVW must lead and motivate cadres, 
workers, and personnel at all sectors and localities to actively 
participate in the struggle against bureaucratism, embezzlement, 
corruption, and other negative phenomena while striving to 
vigorously launch a movement to practice thrift and build the 
