revolutionary Armed Forces, rallied rock-firm behind Supreme 
Commander General Kim Chong-il, would make a thousand-fold 
retaliation against the aggressors, annihilating them at a 
stroke, if they dare to provoke the socialist motherland of 
Korea. 

