<H3> <TI>   Kim Chong-il Sends Birthday Tables to Delegates </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kim Chong-il Sends Birthday Tables to Delegates </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0304085594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0819 GMT 3 Apr 94 </F>
